{"tid":267744,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[JJ插沙求解]有關詩歌押韻問題","createTime":"2017-06-02T13:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T14:37:59.000Z","uid":33604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3fe75247c91a9935c41065f2f899a06556fbf65e","tid":267744,"uid":33604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T13:28:53.000Z","msg":"最近睇到翁卷嘅《鄉村四月》：<br />\n綠遍山原白滿川，子規聲裏雨如煙。<br />\n鄉村四月閒人少，才了蠶桑又插田。<br />\n<br />\n睇到分析話詩歌入面嘅&ldquo;川&rdquo;、&ldquo;煙&rdquo;、&ldquo;田&rdquo;係押韻字<br />\n&ldquo;煙&rdquo;、&ldquo;田&rdquo;押韻我都可以理解，但點解&ldquo;川&rdquo;都係嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704cb6cf7971c6e287a3ff4a9a99aefa1e650499","tid":267744,"uid":33604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T13:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78e3ffeec36c5c9753d3b2ae48fb1bac5565bca","tid":267744,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T14:08:24.000Z","msg":"煲東瓜"},{"pid":"9ecad2539e802777333aefd0e8a53f5fe7bb65f2","tid":267744,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T14:34:24.000Z","msg":"查平水韻 下平: 一先<br />\n唔好靠估"},{"pid":"62f8186608f0a425ec6e2b9a952e7610c8328be2","tid":267744,"uid":120418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T14:37:59.000Z","msg":"因為古代唔係用廣東話<br />\n廣東話只係比普通話更加接近中古音<br />\n所以要用返當時既音去作決定<br />\n可以查下平水韻，睇下係唔係同一韻部"}]}